## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and reports, which may not cover all recent developments in Medicaid strategies. Additionally, the search was limited to English-language sources, potentially excluding relevant international perspectives. The dynamic nature of healthcare policy means that recommendations and strategies may evolve, necessitating ongoing review and analysis.

